    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain the <strong>king prawns</strong></p><p>Once the sauce has thickened slightly, add the <strong>king prawns </strong>to the pan and cook for 4-5 min or until the prawns are cooked through and the sauce has reduced to a thick stew – this is your <strong>pepper & prawn stew</strong></p>",
