    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>mayo </strong>in a small bowl with the <strong>sliced spring onion</strong>, <strong>remaining chipotle</strong> <strong>paste </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!), a drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong> and <strong>half</strong> of the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>coriander </strong>(you'll use the rest later!)</p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>pepper</strong> and set aside – this is your <strong>smoky mayo</strong></p>",
