    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once your potatoes are almost cooked, proceed with this step!</p><p>Heat another pan with a matching lid with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium-low heat</p><p>Crack the <strong>eggs</strong> into a bowl, and once the pan is hot, add the<strong> eggs</strong> in one go</p><p>Cover with a lid and cook for 2-3 min or until done to your liking, then remove from the heat and season with <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p>",
