    {
      "instruction": "<p>Stir the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>chopped coriander</strong> through the<strong> pepper & prawn stew</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>fried</strong> <strong>eggs</strong> over the stew with the <strong>crispy</strong> <strong>potatoes</strong> and <strong>smoky mayo</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
